WEBVTT

00:01.929 --> 00:02.799
Previously on Angel:

00:03.129 --> 00:05.410
There are forces
you know nothing about.

00:06.129 --> 00:08.730
You think I'll stand by
while you finish the game?

00:09.130 --> 00:10.640
Police. Nobody move!

00:14.529 --> 00:16.600
Stay down or they'll kill you.

00:21.129 --> 00:23.379
- Darla, how are you?
- I'm fine, Holland.

00:24.129 --> 00:27.039
They brought her back.
I need to know why. Why human?

00:27.730 --> 00:30.190
You were given a second chance.
Don't throw it away--

00:30.730 --> 00:33.429
- I'm dying.
- Syphilitic heart condition. Terminal.

00:33.729 --> 00:36.119
I won't leave you.
Every moment you have...

00:36.729 --> 00:39.399
...I'll be by your side.
You'll never be alone.

00:45.729 --> 00:47.689
How did you think this would end?

00:49.000 --> 00:55.074
